I know that the Zamarons and their Star Sapphires have been featured
in recent issues of Green Lantern and/or the Green Lantern Corps, and
presumably they will be playing a major roll in the Sinestro Wars.

I also know that the way they've been presented seems to represent a
major retcon of what we've known about them before, very close to an
&quot;everything you've known is WRONG!&quot; situation.

But I haven't been able to track what is now known or implied about
their history and motives. So, on the basis of what we've been shown
to date, can anyone fill me in on:

- The histories of the Zamarons and the Star Sapphires
- What they've been trying to accomplish, and what they're trying to
accomplish now
- What major and/or significant past stories concerning them will
have to be discarded or heavily retconned

Speculations and extrapolations welcome! Let me (us) know what you
THINK is going on....

Thank you one and all.
